| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3555 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6f4bf611-8fc3-5cda-a6f6-906f51bd240c"
